  "text": "For the calculation of all DGI components, the original method by McNaughton et al. [CITATION_1] was exactly replicated with 2 exceptions. Two components, salt use and fluid intake, were excluded from the present calculation of DGI scores, because data on these items were lacking in the Nambour FFQ.",
